com.orientechnologies.orient.core.index

Class OIndexTxAware<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orientechnologies.orient.core.index.OIndexAbstractDelegate<T>
      • com.orientechnologies.orient.core.index.OIndexTxAware<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OIndex<T>, Comparable<OIndex<T>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OIndexTxAwareMultiValue, OIndexTxAwareOneValue

    public abstract class OIndexTxAware<T>
extends OIndexAbstractDelegate<T>
    Transactional wrapper for indexes. Stores changes locally to the transaction until tx.commit(). All the other operations are delegated to the wrapped OIndex instance.
    Author:
    Luca Garulli (l.garulli--(at)--orientdb.com)

      static class  OIndexTxAware.PartialSearchMode
      Indicates search behavior in case of OCompositeKey keys that have less amount of internal keys are used, whether lowest or highest partially matched key should be used.
